content/uploads/2025/01/Perfume-Genius.-Credit-Cody-Critcheloe-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Perfume-Genius.-Credit-Cody-Critcheloe-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Perfume-Genius.-Credit-Cody-Critcheloe-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Perfume-Genius.-Credit-Cody-Critcheloe-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Perfume-Genius">Perfume Genius</a>宣布了他的新专辑《Glory》，并分享了其令人反思的主打单曲《It&#39;s A Mirror》。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong><strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/perfume-genius-ugly-season-review-3248094">香水天才——“丑陋的季节”评论：奖励思想开放的大胆声明</a></strong></li></ul><p>以厚实的民谣摇滚即兴重复开场，在 Perfume Genius（真名 Mike Hadreas）情感柔和的歌声的推动下，这位音乐家用“It&#39;s A Mirror”来反思被压垮并最终陷入孤立循环的情况。</p><p>哈德里亚斯在新闻稿中谈到这首歌时分享道：“即使什么都没有发生，我醒来时也不知所措。我用一天剩下的时间来尝试调节，我更喜欢在家里独自思考。但为什么？他们大多是坏人。几十年来它们也没有真正改变。</p><p> “当我被困在这些孤立的循环中时，我写了《这是一面镜子》，看到外面有一些不同的、甚至可能是美丽的东西，但不太知道如何冒险出去。我有很多保持门关着的练习。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Perfume Genius - “It&#39;s a Mirror”（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hx2_NGaDPrk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>由 Cody Critcheloe 执导，这首歌的音乐视频中，香水天才在一间宽敞的卧室中醒来，然后骑着一辆摩托车，最终发生了车祸。从那里，他穿过一条高速公路，开始被一群骑自行车的人围住。</p><p>他继续走到加油站旁边的一块广告牌前，上面写着“荣耀”一词。他的第二个版本走到加油站，开始给自己加油，然后看着镜头，划一根火柴，然后屏幕变黑。</p><p> 《Glory》由 Perfume Genius 的长期合作者 Blake Mills 制作，涉及“内部和外部之间的来回”。这是哈德里亚斯继 2022 年的《<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/perfume-genius-ugly-season-review-3248094">丑陋季节</a>》之后的第七张专辑。 《Glory》将于 3 月 28 日通过 Matador 发行，并可<a href="https://eu-west-1.protection.sophos.com/?d=mat-r.co&amp;u=aHR0cHM6Ly9wZXJmdW1lZ2VuaXVzLm1hdC1yLmNvL2dsb3J5&amp;p=m&amp;i=NjVmNzQ3NjJhOWQ0MjIwYjkxMWJiOTA3&amp;t=eDlhRCtJQmkvQndRUDBhVURXTEdoRjVGTnJTcm5XMm1OV3ZRYlhVMnhaZz0=&amp;h=f171fd54b65c410b8df556b21857a45e&amp;s=AVNPUEhUT0NFTkNSWVBUSVbzGtPb2GocY4BnjPz2KLhxsj4b2IB83LprbKnY0icCmyrrsh9s70o9hUpofv3XROtsGsdO7tL7kTEas1Z2SWehI1jmV-mTtc6pMY85VssDtw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订。 </p><figure id="attachment_3829257" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829257" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829257" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Perfume-Genius-GLORY-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Perfume Genius &#39;GLORY&#39; 专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Perfume-Genius-GLORY-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Perfume-Genius-GLORY-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Perfume-Genius-GLORY-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Perfume-Genius-GLORY-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Perfume-Genius-GLORY-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Perfume-Genius-GLORY-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Perfume-Genius-GLORY-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829257" class="wp-caption-text"> Perfume Genius &#39;GLORY&#39; 专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>《荣耀》的曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>1.“这是一面镜子”</strong><br /> <strong>2.“没有门牙”（壮举。奥尔德斯·哈丁）</strong><br /> <strong>3.“清净心”</strong><br /> <strong>4.《我与天使》</strong><br /> <strong>5.《留给明天》</strong><br /> <strong>6.“全力以赴”</strong><br /> <strong>7.“卡佩齐奥”</strong><br /> <strong>8.“迪翁”</strong><br /> <strong>9.“连续”</strong><br /> <strong>10.“闲逛”</strong><br /> <strong>11.《荣耀》</strong></p><p>在其他地方，Perfume Genius 还宣布进行广泛的北美巡演以支持这张专辑。 Perfume Genius 将于 5 月 12 日在加利福尼亚州希尔兹堡的 Little Saint 出发，穿越北美，在旧金山、菲尼克斯、图森、奥斯汀、达拉斯、华盛顿、布鲁克林、波士顿、布法罗、多伦多、克利夫兰等城市停留以及更多内容，然后于 6 月 27 日结束在波特兰革命大厅的巡演。</p><p>艺术家预售将于当地时间明天（1 月 16 日）上午 10 点开始，面向<a href="https://eu-west-1.protection.sophos.com/?d=perfumegenius.org&amp;u=aHR0cDovL3BlcmZ1bWVnZW5pdXMub3JnLw==&amp;p=m&amp;i=NjVmNzQ3NjJhOWQ0MjIwYjkxMWJiOTA3&amp;t=YmdXdmdFakF4WkxTckNOUzJSbjFuMGF3b09uNEJSVDZYVnd1Q3lPQ3RCND0=&amp;h=9cd4347da46448e2a906246d85adb0ad&amp;s=AVNPUEhUT0NFTkNSWVBUSVZDYCacqntyfEzCu55-tt8VarrxmRjFDsm7gEbAZu8jKw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此报名的</a>观众。一般门票销售将于当地时间周五（1 月 17 日）上午 10 点开始。请访问<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fperfume-genius-tickets%2Fartist%2F1451861" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>购买门票并查看下面的完整日期列表。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DE2VaUwv0pF/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="