, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/TheLotteryWinners-postpone-album-release-date-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/TheLotteryWinners-postpone-album-release-date-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/TheLotteryWinners-postpone-album-release-date-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/TheLotteryWinners-postpone-album-release-date-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-lottery-winners">The Lottery Winners</a>以“制造挑战”为由推迟了新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lottery-winners-announce-their-new-studio-album-koko-with-playful-single-you-again-featuring-reverend-the-makers-jon-mcclure-3796572">《KOKO》</a>的发行。</p><p>这支曼彻斯特独立乐队最初定于 2 月 21 日通过摩登天空发行他们的第六张录音室唱片。其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-turner">Frank Turner</a> （《污垢与黄金》）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nickelback">Nickleback</a>的 Chad Kroeger（《布偶》）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shed-seven">Shed Seven</a> （《天花板》）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/reverend-and-the-makers">Reverend &amp; The Makers</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lottery-winners-announce-their-new-studio-album-koko-with-playful-single-you-again-featuring-reverend-the-makers-jon-mcclure-3796572">《你又来了》</a> ）。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lottery-winners-interview-kate-nash-row-working-class-arts-koko-album-robbie-williams-3821969">彩票中奖者反思凯特·纳什的争论：“她非常出色地强调了工人阶级在艺术方面缺乏机会”</a></strong></li></ul><p>现在，该乐队已经确认，粉丝们需要再等一段时间才能听到完整的 LP，该专辑是继<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-lottery-winners-beat-nines-jessie-ware-and-the-national-to-claim-uk-number-one-album-3440003">他们的第一张英国冠军专辑 2023 年的《焦虑替代疗法》</a>之后推出的。</p><p> “由于制造方面的挑战，我们做出了艰难的决定，将即将推出的专辑《KOKO》的发行推迟四个星期，”彩票中奖者在社交媒体上的一份声明中写道。</p><p> “新的发布日期是 2025 年 3 月 21 日，我们正在倒计时，直到您可以拥有它。”</p><p>他们继续说道：“我们对这张唱片感到无比自豪，这是我们迄今为止最好的作品，对于稍微的延迟，我们深表歉意。我们保证值得等待。继续继续（等待）。汤姆，凯特，罗布和乔。”</p><p>为了使我们兴起，彩票获奖者将在本周五（1月17日）（1月17日）发行“ Dirt and Gold”（Feat。FrankTurner）。您可以通过<a href="https://thelotterywinners.os.fan/dirtandgoldpre-save" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预示制</a>曲目的预览片段。</p><p>查看下面的帖子。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEzUqiqtiNx/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.88